    <header>
      <h6 class="de-u-textGrow2"
          id="ProductInfo-1"
          itemprop="name">
        Resistant materials
      </h6>
    </header>
    <p class="de-u-spaceNone" itemprop="value">This polyamide canvas uses 20
    denier thread, resists 20,000 cycles of abrasion. Martindale test, Standard
    12 947-2 Outer: 100% polyamide 1.4 oz/sqm, 20 denier fabric Lining: 100%
    polyamide fabric (1.2oz/sqm), a mix of 15 and 20 denier threads</p>
  </section>

  <section class="ProductInformation-entry de-u-spaceBottom6"
       aria-labelledby="ProductInfo-2"
