    <header>
      <h6 class="de-u-textGrow2"
          id="ProductInfo-9"
          itemprop="name">
        Product Testing
      </h6>
    </header>
    <p class="de-u-spaceNone" itemprop="value">In November 2017, 6 backpackers
    (4 men and 2 women) with part of the Forclaz design team tested this down
    jacket for 4 days in the Southern French Alps. We were able to make the
    final modifications and validate it for use in mountain backpacking.</p>
  </section>

